<div style="font-size: 300%; text-align: center; padding: 0.1em; font-variant: small-caps; color:black"><span style="font-size:70%;">The</span> Politics of the United Kingdom <span style="font-size:70%;">Portal</span></div>
<div align="center" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:89%;">This is a sister portal of the <a href="Portal_United_Kingdom" title="Portal:United Kingdom">United Kingdom Portal</a></div>
<div id="politics_browsebar" style="margin-top:-3px; margin-bottom:0.2em; text-align:center; font-size:95%;">
<p><small><span style="" title="Featured Article"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Featured_article_star.svg" class="image" title="Featured article"><img alt="Featured article" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Featured_article_star.svg/16px-Featured_article_star.svg.png" width="16" height="16" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Featured_article_star.svg/24px-Featured_article_star.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Featured_article_star.svg/32px-Featured_article_star.svg.png 2x" /></a></span>&#160;<a href="Portal_Politics" title="Portal:Politics">Politics</a>: <a href="Portal_Anarchism" title="Portal:Anarchism">Anarchism</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="Portal_Communism" title="Portal:Communism">Communism</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <span style="" title="Featured Article"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Featured_article_star.svg" class="image" title="Featured article"><img alt="Featured article" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Featured_article_star.svg/16px-Featured_article_star.svg.png" width="16" height="16" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Featured_article_star.svg/24px-Featured_article_star.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Featured_article_star.svg/32px-Featured_article_star.svg.png 2x" /></a></span> <a href="Portal_Conservatism" title="Portal:Conservatism">Conservatism</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="Portal_Fascism" title="Portal:Fascism">Fascism</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="Portal_Liberalism" title="Portal:Liberalism">Liberalism</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="Portal_Libertarianism" title="Portal:Libertarianism">Libertarianism</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="Portal_Political_science" title="Portal:Political science">Political science</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="Portal_Socialism" title="Portal:Socialism">Socialism</a></small></p>
